metadata.name: Kick.
metadata.description:
Skateboarding was my first love, 
getting lost in the ocean of pavement that exists all around us, at any given moment.

Eb & Flow.

Kick & Push. 

Many lessons to be learned. 

Kick // Push is a multichain release, telling the story of being a forever nimble skateboarder, hoping over the fences of any blockchain to skate the empty swimming pools of opportunity that exist on the other side.

This is Kick.
